<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id8f2ce933-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—Subsec. (c). <ref href="/us/pl/115/232">Pub. L. 115–232</ref> substituted “section 2101(12)” for “section 2101(11a)”.</p>
